Ingredients.1: 1 (12.5 fl oz) can chunky shredded chicken (such as Tyson®)

Ingredients.2: 1 (10.75 ounce) can  condensed cream of mushroom soup

Ingredients.3: 1 (10 ounce) package frozen mixed vegetables (such as Birds Eye® Steamfresh®)

Ingredients.4: 1 (10 ounce) can refrigerated small biscuits (such as Pillsbury®)

Directions.1: Preheat the oven to 350 degrees F (175 degrees C).

Directions.2: Mix chicken, soup, and vegetables together in an 8-inch square baking dish. Separate biscuits and place on top to cover filling.

Directions.3: Bake in the preheated oven until biscuits are browned, about 30 minutes.
